<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Up Slightly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, December 29 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange on Tuesday closed at 1535.02, up 0.19 points.
</P>
<P>
A total of 12,708,357 shares changed hands and turnover stood
at 77.96 billion rials (about 12.99 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 16 companies made gains while those of 20 others
declined. 
</P>
</TEXT>
