<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, December 29 (Xinhua) -- Russia is deeply concerned
about the volatile situation in the Great Lakes Region,
especially that in the Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC).
</P>
<P>
This is contained in talks between Russian Ambassador to
Uganda Rudolf Alexeyev and Ugandan State Minister in charge of
International Cooperation Kiddu Makubuya here Tuesday, Radio
Uganda reported.
</P>
<P>
