the Parliamentary Building, focused on issues pertaining to
Uganda's position in the DRC and stability in the region.
</P>
<P>
The minister informed the ambassador of the resolutions that
were reached on the DRC conflict during the Franco-African summit
in Paris in November this year, the report said.
</P>
<P>
The Russian diplomat told his host that Russia considers
reasonable the declaration by the U.N. Security Council that
recommends the countries of Central Africa cancel or suspend the
regional economic sanctions against Burundi. 
