<HEADLINE> Foreign Exchange Rates in Thailand </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 30 (Xinhua) -- The following are foreign
exchange rates against the baht hereon Wednesday as offered by the
Bangkok Bank:
</P>
<P>
